	ArtyIF

[color=#ff6000]Sounds[/color]
	[color=#ff6000]Chrysler LHS tire squeal 04 (04-25-2009).wav[/color] by [color=#ff6000]audible-edge[/color] -- [url]https://freesound.org/s/71739/[/url]
		[color=#ff6000]License:[/color] CC0 1.0 ([url]https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/[/url])
		[color=#ff6000]Changes made:[/color] Trimmed and looped, EQd to remove engine noise, converted to OGG
	[color=#ff6000]Collision 1[/color] by [color=#ff6000]JustInvoke[/color] -- [url]https://freesound.org/s/446126/[/url]
		[color=#ff6000]License:[/color] CC BY 4.0 ([url]https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/[/url])
		[color=#ff6000]Changes made:[/color] Converted to OGG
	[color=#ff6000]Collision 2[/color] by [color=#ff6000]JustInvoke[/color] -- [url]https://freesound.org/s/446125/[/url]
		[color=#ff6000]License:[/color] CC BY 4.0 ([url]https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/[/url])
		[color=#ff6000]Changes made:[/color] Converted to OGG
	[color=#ff6000]Collision 3[/color] by [color=#ff6000]JustInvoke[/color] -- [url]https://freesound.org/s/446132/[/url]
		[color=#ff6000]License:[/color] CC BY 4.0 ([url]https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/[/url])
		[color=#ff6000]Changes made:[/color] Converted to OGG
	[color=#ff6000]metal plate scratch[/color] by [color=#ff6000]Ridderick[/color] -- [url]https://freesound.org/s/707639/[/url]
		[color=#ff6000]License:[/color] CC0 1.0 ([url]https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/[/url])
		[color=#ff6000]Changes made:[/color] Trimmed and looped, converted to OGG
