	[color=#ff6000]Car Brakes sqeak screech squeal stop.wav[/color] by [color=#ff6000]WavJunction.com[/color] -- [url]https://freesound.org/s/456764/[/url]
		[color=#ff6000]License:[/color] CC0 1.0 ([url]https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/[/url])
